data.text:
Welcome Home

We invite you and your family to join us for our next worship service! When you come to Pathway, you can expect to be welcomed into a friendly environment by real people who are genuinely excited to see you. Our services last about an hour, are filled with great music, and include an inspiring message from the Bible by our pastor.

Worship Services every Sunday at 10:00am

We Can't Wait To Meet You

Pathway Church of God is located in the heart of the Brooklyn/Curtis Bay Area of Baltimore, MD. This community-focused ministry has been a beacon of hope to its neighbors since 1946. Founded as a part of the Church of God (Cleveland, Tennessee) denomination, Pathway is known for its Spirit-filled worship, passionate preaching about Jesus, and enthusiasm for God.

Pastor Billy & Sarah Humphrey have lead this congregation for over 22 years. They have three children, Seth, Luke, and Lela, who have been a part of this church for their entire lives. As a family, they love camping, hiking, family game night, and going out to eat eating together. Pastor Billy is an avid sports fanâespecially for the Ravens. Sarah leads worship onÂ Sundays and teaches in Anne Arundel County as an Elementary Music Teacher.
